xml-api
=======

  XML::API is a class for creating XML documents using object method
  calls. This class is meant for generating XML programatically and not
  for reading or parsing it.

INSTALLATION

  To install this module type the following:

     perl Makefile.PL
     make
     make test
     make install

DEPENDENCIES

  If they following modules are available they may be used, but they
  are not necessary for normal usage:

     HTML::Parse      (CPAN)

